NK010(tha)019:0: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje phur pa rgyud lugs kyi
NK010(tha)019:1: smad las dam can nye bar bsnyen pa'i man ngag
NK010(tha)019:2: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i zhal lung zhes bya ba gsang
NK010(tha)019:4: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)019:5: spyi don gnyis pa smad las dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i
NK010(tha)019:6: sa bcad la dam can nye bar bsnyen pa dang
NK010(tha)019:7: / ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa'o //
NK010(tha)019:8: dang po ni rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NK010(tha)019:9: yal ga med pa'i b+han d+ha ni /
NK010(tha)019:13: yugs sa mo yi mngal khrag gis //
NK010(tha)019:15: phrin las bzhi yi dbyibs bya'o //
NK010(tha)019:16: de la dgra bgegs ming byang gzhug /
NK010(tha)019:17: bsnyen pa'i phur pas gzir la bzhag /
NK010(tha)019:18: gtor ma sman dang rak+tara bcas //
NK010(tha)019:19: zhes pas rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor las ches dma' ba'i
NK010(tha)019:20: lho nub mtshams su srung ma'i stegs bu gru gsum
NK010(tha)019:21: nag po'i lto ba'ang gru gsum du brus pa'i thod
NK010(tha)019:22: pa la / re kh+aa gru gsum mthing nag zla gam dmar po /
NK010(tha)019:24: sgo rnams dur khrod mi ros spungs pa'i mtha' lcags ri nag po me ri dang bcas bris pa'am /
NK010(tha)019:25: yang na sgo snam spangs pa'i nang du gdab pa drug gi las dang 'brel na snga ma las /
NK010(tha)019:26: khrag dang dug dang sna tshogs byug /
NK010(tha)019:27: dri ma dag las ling+ga ni //
NK010(tha)019:28: thod pa'i nang du bskyed par bya //
NK010(tha)019:29: lcags sna lnga tshang sras mchog gcig /
NK010(tha)019:30: sngags bris dbang bskur byin rlabs gzug /
NK010(tha)019:31: ces pas rdzas kyi bca' gcan bzhag cing dam can
NK010(tha)019:32: nye bsnyen tsam la zan ling la phur pa gzug
NK010(tha)019:33: / mtha' skor du sman raka gtor gsum /
NK010(tha)019:35: sba 'khar tshigs gsum la bse byang dkar nag sku dang snying pos mtshan pa dang /
NK010(tha)019:37: lug dkar nag gi thod pa /
NK010(tha)019:42: mi rta myur du bsad pa'i khrag dang /
NK010(tha)019:44: mar gyi mtsho la sogs pa'i mthun rdzas kyang bsham /
NK010(tha)019:45: lha bsnyen gzhung bsrang ba nas bzlas pa'i bar rdzogs par byas rjes /
NK010(tha)019:46: gzhan yang thod pa'i gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)019:47: sras bcas dam can bcas pa bskyed //
NK010(tha)019:49: bsnyen phur ni mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa dkyil
NK010(tha)019:50: 'khor yongs rdzogs kyi bdag nyid dregs pa dbang du
NK010(tha)019:51: sdud pa'i gnyen po yin pas /
NK010(tha)019:52: lcum gzhogs ldir ba'i nang du gzhal med khang rdzogs
NK010(tha)019:53: pa la gtso bo yab yum dang lcum gzhogs brgyad
NK010(tha)019:54: la phyogs mtshams kyi khro bo yab yum mgo brnyan
NK010(tha)019:55: dang bcas pa / rgya mdud gong 'og nang h+aum k+aar stobs chen yab yum /
NK010(tha)019:57: dbal gyi ngam la phur srung bcu gnyis /
NK010(tha)019:58: ming po las mkhan dang bcas pa rdzogs par bskyed nas spyan drang ba ni /
NK010(tha)019:60: stong gsum 'di na dregs pa can //
NK010(tha)019:61: sus kyang dam la ma chud pa //
NK010(tha)019:62: rdo rje gzhon nu'i bka' la sdod //
NK010(tha)019:63: ma mo mkha' 'gro yongs kyi gtso //
NK010(tha)019:64: dam can ma mo bcu gnyis dang //
NK010(tha)019:65: rang rang rigs kyi ming po ni //
NK010(tha)019:66: khams gsum srog la dbang za zhing //
NK010(tha)019:67: glo bur ye 'drog bdag po ste //
NK010(tha)019:68: srid pa skos 'debs rgyal po dang //
NK010(tha)019:69: e ka dza ti bshos pa'i sras //
NK010(tha)019:70: shwa na spyan gcig mched bzhi dang //
NK010(tha)019:71: ming po shel ging dkar por bcas //
NK010(tha)019:72: ri rgyal lhun po'i steng shed na //
NK010(tha)019:73: dug mtsho mer ba'i nang shed na //
NK010(tha)019:74: dung mkhar dkar po'i nang nas gshegs //
NK010(tha)019:75: bdud nag yab yum rol pa'i sras //
NK010(tha)019:76: lang+ka mgrin bcu'i chung ma'i tshul //
NK010(tha)019:77: nag mo re ti mched bzhi dang //
NK010(tha)019:78: ming po ma h+aa k+aa la bcas //
NK010(tha)019:79: ri rab chen po'i byang shar mtshams //
NK010(tha)019:80: mu le mthing gi mtsho nang gi //
NK010(tha)019:81: lcags mkhar nag po'i nang nas gshegs //
NK010(tha)019:82: gnod sbyin zangs mdog rgyal po dang //
NK010(tha)019:83: yum gcig zangs mgrin ldem pa'i sras //
NK010(tha)019:84: bswe yi lha mo mched bzhi dang //
NK010(tha)019:85: ming po bse yi skyes bur bcas //
NK010(tha)019:86: ri rab chen po'i lho nub mtshams //
NK010(tha)019:87: bse mtsho mer ba'i dbus shed nas //
NK010(tha)019:88: bswe mkhar smug po'i nang nas gshegs //
NK010(tha)019:89: re ti nag la bswe mo dmar //
NK010(tha)019:90: shwa na dkar ldem ming po ser //
NK010(tha)019:91: kun kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis la //
NK010(tha)019:92: legs nyes stangs 'dzin bdag po ste //
NK010(tha)019:93: lcags kyus 'gugs shing phur bus sgrol //
NK010(tha)019:94: bzhon pa can dang rkyang pa'i tshul //
NK010(tha)019:95: rnam 'gyur ma nges cir yang ston //
NK010(tha)019:96: ma mo bdun dang sring mo bzhi //
NK010(tha)019:97: dregs pa chen po drug la sogs //
NK010(tha)019:98: sprul pa yang sprul bsam mi khyab //
NK010(tha)019:99: khyed rnams srog snying nga la yod //
NK010(tha)019:100: sngon tshe dpal chen khrag 'thung gis //
NK010(tha)019:101: ji ltar dam la bzhag pa bzhin //
NK010(tha)019:102: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba dang //
NK010(tha)019:103: dkon mchog dbu 'phang bstod pa dang //
NK010(tha)019:104: nyams pa bdun po bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)019:105: dam can ma g.yel dam la 'dus //
NK010(tha)019:106: gang la dmigs pa khyod kyis shes //
NK010(tha)019:107: rlung las myur ba'i stabs kyis gshegs //
NK010(tha)019:108: badz+ra kro d+ha tsit+ta ma h+aa li shu ra shu ra /
NK010(tha)019:111: shu la tsi p+aa ra shu par ni /
NK010(tha)019:112: yo ga shud+d+ha tsit+ta ma ra li /
NK010(tha)019:113: kro d+ha yo gi n+ai badz+ra /
NK010(tha)019:115: sha sha ni dza dzah dam bzhag ni /
NK010(tha)019:117: bam ril thod pa'i gzhal yas nang //
NK010(tha)019:118: mthun rdzas spyan gzigs tshang zhing mdzes //
NK010(tha)019:119: dam can bzhugs shing chags pa'i gnas //
NK010(tha)019:120: dam tshig nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK010(tha)019:121: thams cad dam tshig chos shes na //
NK010(tha)019:122: ye shes lha dang mnyam par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)019:123: sa ma ya m+aa ma tam na rak+kana /
NK010(tha)019:124: zhes bdud rtsi blud la dam bsre bya /
NK010(tha)019:125: de nas gtor ma 'bul ba ni /
NK010(tha)019:127: dmar gyi gtor ma chen po rang rang 'dod pa'i
NK010(tha)019:128: longs spyod kyi sprin du 'char ba 'di nyid bsngo
NK010(tha)019:129: ba'i gnas su gyur pa ni bcom ldan 'das rdo
NK010(tha)019:130: rje phur pa'i bka' sdod dam can ma mo bcu
NK010(tha)019:131: gnyis ming po sprul 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la
NK010(tha)019:132: 'bul lo // lcags kyi spyang mo dang lcags kyi khyi mo la zhon pa'i shwa na ma gnyis /
NK010(tha)019:134: zangs kyi wa mo la zhon pa'i sri la ma
NK010(tha)019:135: gnyis te mu kha chen mo mched bzhi'i zhal du
NK010(tha)019:136: 'bul lo // dz+wa la dz+wa la badz+ra ma ma
NK010(tha)019:137: muk+ta la ye dza ya du man d+hi shwa ri
NK010(tha)019:138: n+ai la pu tsi h+aum b+h+yo h+aum i dam b+ha
NK010(tha)019:139: ling ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)019:140: phyi nam zla dus bzhi la dbang byed pa'i bdag nyid chen mo bzhi'i zhal du 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)019:142: trag rak+sha ma ti he dun b+h+yo /
NK010(tha)019:143: ma h+aa yak+sha na ga ma he dun b+h+yo /
NK010(tha)019:144: i dam b+ha ling ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)019:145: bswe mo nyis brgya lnga bcu'i dbang mo sa bdag ma bzhi'i zhal du 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)019:146: ka tam ka te dza ye bi dza ye a
NK010(tha)019:147: dzi te a pa ra tsi ta su ki b+ha
NK010(tha)019:148: ya b+ha ra tsit+tam yo g+ai shwa ri ya tsit+ta
NK010(tha)019:149: h+aum phata i dam b+ha ling ta kha kha kh+aa
NK010(tha)019:150: hi kh+aa hi / dpal ldan mgon po chen po'i zhal du 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)019:151: k+aa la ma tram ma h+aa k+aa la ra ti ye k+aa la r+au pa h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)019:152: i dam b+ha ling ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)019:153: bswe'i skyes bu'i zhal du 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)019:154: m+aa ra sa ni ra sha ni ra sha b+hi kun lan shu lan h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)019:155: i dam b+ha ling ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)019:156: rgyal po shel ging gi zhal du 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)019:157: k+aa ra ma k+aa ra ya /
NK010(tha)019:158: tsi tra pa la tri la thun i dam b+ha ling ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)019:159: ma bdun sring bzhi'i zhal du 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)019:160: h+aum ma ma pa shi ku ru ma tang nya ka ra i nan /
NK010(tha)019:161: i dam b+ha ling ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)019:162: dregs pa sde drug gi zhal du 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)019:163: d+ha d+hi ma ma shi kram karma kat+ye ya /
NK010(tha)019:165: i dam b+ha ling ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)019:166: bzhes nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs /
NK010(tha)019:169: phrin las rnam pa bzhi sgrubs /
NK010(tha)019:172: khyad par du yang bal yul yang le shod du
NK010(tha)019:173: rig 'dzin chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi bka' dang
NK010(tha)019:174: dam la bzhag / rdo rje phur pa'i srung mar dbang bskur /
NK010(tha)019:175: srog snying mdongs gsol du phul nas ji ltar khas blangs pa'i dam tshig gnyan po dran par mdzod /
NK010(tha)019:176: rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa dang de 'dzin gyi
NK010(tha)019:177: skyes bu dam pa rnams la log par blta zhing
NK010(tha)019:178: nyams pa bdun dang bcas pa'i dgra bgegs rnams ltas
NK010(tha)019:179: dang cho 'phrul sna tshogs pas spa bkong la /
NK010(tha)019:180: drag shul gyi las la mngon du spyod pas thal ba'i rdul phran bzhin du brlag par mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)019:181: ces dam tshig bsgrags shing phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK010(tha)019:183: rgya bal gnyis kyi mtshams shed na //
NK010(tha)019:184: dgun yang me tog pad+ma skye //
NK010(tha)019:185: chu yang byang chub bdud rtsi chu //
NK010(tha)019:186: yang le shod kyi brag phug tu //
NK010(tha)019:187: phur pa grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyis //
NK010(tha)019:188: bka' dang dam la bzhag pa ni //
NK010(tha)019:189: dam can lha mo bcu gnyis te //
NK010(tha)019:190: dngos gcig la yang mtshan stong ma //
NK010(tha)019:192: shwa na mu kha mched bzhir ston //
NK010(tha)019:193: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu dang //
NK010(tha)019:194: lcags kyi khyi mo mtshal mig can //
NK010(tha)019:195: zangs kyi wa mo rkang gsum dang //
NK010(tha)019:196: gser gyi 'phar ba lce brgyad steng //
NK010(tha)019:197: mi mo'i lus la phra men gdong //
NK010(tha)019:198: sprul pa yang sprul bsam mi khyab //
NK010(tha)019:200: bdag nyid chen mo mched bzhir ston //
NK010(tha)019:201: re ma ti dang re ma du //
NK010(tha)019:202: re ma dza dang re ma dzu //
NK010(tha)019:203: khyung drel sha ba chu glang zhon //
NK010(tha)019:204: bar snang kun la dbang bsgyur nas //
NK010(tha)019:205: nam zla dus bzhi'i bdag po mdzad //
NK010(tha)019:206: rang rgyud can du ston pa ni //
NK010(tha)019:207: sa bdag bswe yi lha mo ste //
NK010(tha)019:208: tsha ba rong na bzhugs pa'i tshe //
NK010(tha)019:209: de byin gza' yi bu mo ser //
NK010(tha)019:210: zhag gi mtsho la mnga' dbang mdzad //
NK010(tha)019:211: chibs ni gza' rta zhur po chibs //
NK010(tha)019:212: shu lan d+ha ri srog gi snying //
NK010(tha)019:213: mang yul so na bzhugs pa ni //
NK010(tha)019:214: rak+ta'i mtsho la mnga' dbang mdzad //
NK010(tha)019:215: bswe byin btsan gyi bu mo dmar //
NK010(tha)019:216: chibs su btsan rta dmar po chibs //
NK010(tha)019:217: tsa mun da ri srog gi snying //
NK010(tha)019:218: snye nam yul na bzhugs pa ni //
NK010(tha)019:219: phag byin klu yi bu mo ljang //
NK010(tha)019:220: chibs su klu rta ljang gu chibs //
NK010(tha)019:221: ki kang da ri srog gi snying //
NK010(tha)019:222: bal yul mthil na bzhugs pa ni //
NK010(tha)019:223: ya byin bdud kyi bu mo mthing //
NK010(tha)019:224: mar khu'i mtsho la mnga' dbang mdzad //
NK010(tha)019:225: chibs su bdud rta mthing nag chibs //
NK010(tha)019:226: ku ma da ra srog gi snying //
NK010(tha)019:227: kun kyang rang mdog ber chen gsol //
NK010(tha)019:228: ral pa phur pa'i lan tshar can //
NK010(tha)019:229: ming po'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)019:232: bran dang pho nya bka' nyan tshogs //
NK010(tha)019:233: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK010(tha)019:234: nga yi spyan sngar khas blangs bzhin //
NK010(tha)019:235: phyi rabs rnal 'byor phrin las kyi //
NK010(tha)019:236: bstan par dgra 'dre byung ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)019:237: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)019:238: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)019:239: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)019:240: dregs pa mang po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)019:241: khyed kyi mthun rtsal rab tu dbyung //
NK010(tha)019:242: sangs rgyas bstan pa bshig pa dang //
NK010(tha)019:243: dkon cog sku dgra dben rtsa 'joms //
NK010(tha)019:244: chos khrims 'dral dang slob dpon dgra //
NK010(tha)019:246: bsad dang dbab dang nad ngan gyis //
NK010(tha)019:247: ji nas brlag par khyed kyis gyis //
NK010(tha)019:248: de nas bzhi snying gcig tu dril ba'i bzlas pa
NK010(tha)019:249: ni mi mthun pa mang du snang yang rnal 'byor
NK010(tha)019:250: chen po'i le'u dgu pa las /
NK010(tha)019:251: bzlas pa dpal bo gcig pa'i sngags //
NK010(tha)019:252: dang po bcom ldan phur pa'i rdzas //
NK010(tha)019:253: thams cad 'dus dang ri rab dang //
NK010(tha)019:254: mnan pa khro bo 'dus pa dang //
NK010(tha)019:255: gong bzhin dam can 'dus pa dang //
NK010(tha)019:256: thabs dang shes rab ging mchog dang //
NK010(tha)019:257: rtog pa las kyi sngags bcas pa //
NK010(tha)019:258: rnam bzhi tshang ba bzhi snying ste //
NK010(tha)019:259: dpa' bo gcig la ngal ba med par bzlas //
NK010(tha)019:260: zhes pas don le'u bcu gsum pa nas gsal bar bstan pa ni /
NK010(tha)019:261: dang po bdag nyid 'bru bdun dang //
NK010(tha)019:262: de 'og phyag rgya mnan yig gsum //
NK010(tha)019:263: ming rung yi ge gzas par bshad //
NK010(tha)019:264: shwa na'i yi ge bcu drug dang //
NK010(tha)019:265: re ma ti yi rtsa sngags dang //
NK010(tha)019:266: bswe mo'i snying po bcu bdun dang //
NK010(tha)019:267: 'khor ba rtsad gcod yi ge dgu //
NK010(tha)019:268: thams cad tshang ba'i yi ge bdun //
NK010(tha)019:269: dril te rab tu bzlas pa yin //
NK010(tha)019:270: mdangs dang bral bar rab tu nges //
NK010(tha)019:272: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dz+wa la nam /
NK010(tha)019:273: dzahh+aum bam hoh slob dpon rnam gsum gyi dgongs pa dang 'bum 'grel ltar yin /
NK010(tha)019:279: d+ha ti ma ma karma i dam ma tam nya
NK010(tha)019:280: ka ra dza ye bi dza ye a tsi te
NK010(tha)019:281: a pa ra tsi te ka tam ka te ma
NK010(tha)019:282: ra s+ya na pra ma rta na ye sarba big
NK010(tha)019:284: ces ye shes kyi lha dang srung ma thams cad
NK010(tha)019:285: kyi srog snying 'dus pa'i d+ha ti 'bring po spu
NK010(tha)019:286: gri dang dbye ba legs par chod pa 'di dmigs
NK010(tha)019:287: gnad dang ldan par chig sgril du bzlas pas srog
NK010(tha)019:288: chags mang po bsad pa dang /
NK010(tha)019:289: bya skad 'tsher ba sogs spyi'i rtags dang /
NK010(tha)019:290: sgos rtags su gcan gzan gyi tshogs rmi na shwa na ma nye /
NK010(tha)019:291: mo btsun dang nag mo dang bya nag dre'u rta
NK010(tha)019:292: so bya la sogs byung na bdag nyid ma nye
NK010(tha)019:296: nya sbrul byung na bse mo nye /
NK010(tha)019:298: rta pa'i tshogs rmi na skyes bu ging nye bas nye ba la mthil gtad /
NK010(tha)019:299: de ni phyi d+ha ti ltar bsgrub pa ste /
NK010(tha)019:300: gzhan du na rtsa rgyud las /
NK010(tha)019:301: d+ha ti 'dus pa bsdu yig gsum //
NK010(tha)019:302: ngan sngags yin par nga yis bshad //
NK010(tha)019:305: gsang ba bsdu yig ltar bsgrub pa'i tshul slob dpon rnam gsum gyi man ngag tu shes par bya'o //
NK010(tha)019:307: lha la bstod cing srung ma bskul //
NK010(tha)019:308: de nas bsnyen pa'i dus su ste //
NK010(tha)019:309: rtags tshang gnyis med dngos grub blang //
NK010(tha)019:310: zhes pas dam can bod pa'i rtags tshang nas bskul ba ni gtor ma bzang po bshams la /
NK010(tha)019:313: dpal gyi pho nya'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)019:315: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)019:316: ces bskul mthar tshogs tha ma dang 'brel bar ling+ga bstab pa bya /
NK010(tha)019:317: lhag ma btang la dngos grub lha las blang ba'i tshul gzhung bzhin nam /
NK010(tha)019:318: rgyas par rang gzhung gi tshe'i cho ga dang 'brel bar blang ba nyid zab bo //
NK010(tha)019:319: gnyis pa ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa ni /
NK010(tha)019:321: drag po bsad pa'i las bya ba //
NK010(tha)019:322: nyi nag mar gyi ngo la ni //
NK010(tha)019:323: drag po las kyi rim pa bya //
NK010(tha)019:324: gdab sngags drug gi las byas la //
NK010(tha)019:325: dam can sngags dang bcas pa dang //
NK010(tha)019:326: gzhi snying sngags la ming btags la //
NK010(tha)019:327: bzlas tshad tshe lung khrus lung gis //
NK010(tha)019:328: phur gdab rdul du brlag par bya //
NK010(tha)019:329: zhal du bstab cing gtor ma btang //
NK010(tha)019:330: las gsum nges pas las mtha' brtul //
NK010(tha)019:331: de la rtags mtshan med pa na //
NK010(tha)019:332: yi dam nar ma gzhung du bya'o //
NK010(tha)019:333: las kyi rim pa rdzogs byas pas //
NK010(tha)019:334: gang la dmigs pa gdon mi za //
NK010(tha)019:335: zhes pas phur pa grub na gdab las bya ba'i don gzhan du shes par bya zhing /
NK010(tha)019:336: dngos grub dgra las blang ba'i man ngag nyams su bstar ro //
NK010(tha)019:337: 'di ni rgyud la man ngag lhan thabs su bsnan pa'i lugs su shes par bya'o //
